room_title: Escape room "Western Bank Heist" by Locks and Puzzles Escape Room in Toms River
room_description: You and your fellow outlaws have been wandering the desert in search of food, water, and supplies. All of a sudden you stumble upon a quaint little town in the middle of the Wild West.  It sure is quiet as the townspeople are out rounding up their cattle. Now do as outlaws do, rob the bank and make a quick getaway before you are caught dead in the act!
